title: Ep. 117 - Kavanaugh Backfiring Big Time on Democrats
description:
The Democrats were heading into the midterms in a pretty good position. But they've overplayed their hand with Kavanaugh. Their disgusting and dishonest behavior has caused conservatives to rally together. Conservatives haven't been this united in a very long time. That's bad news for Democrats.
